IMPORTANT DEPLOYMENT NOTICE

This is a REFERENCE IMPLEMENTATION demonstrating the system architecture and
workflows specified in "Nepal Government Digital HR Management System —
Complete Integrated Reference (PSC + MoFAGA, April 2026)". Before deploying
against real civil service data, the following production hardening items
are required:

  - Replace simulated DSC with real X.509 PKI bound to Nepal Government NID
  - Wire a licensed SMS gateway (NTC/NCell) for real OTP dispatch
  - Configure MongoDB with TLS, authentication, and replica sets
  - Rotate JWT secrets; consider short-lived tokens with refresh
  - Rate-limit auth endpoints
  - Terminate TLS at ingress (nginx/ALB/Cloudflare)
  - Review audit log retention policy per Civil Service Act amendment
  - Integrate real NID and National Health Registry APIs under the Data
    Protection Act

See README.md §12 (Production deployment notes) for the full list.
